{"tid":2447739,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獲派公屋不再與家婆同住惹爭議 　內地來港婦反駁：排了7年隊","createTime":"2021-03-15T11:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T16:15:54.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c08442e1bd7cb29fd78e461a2f4214acf6d3c2","tid":2447739,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/none/ed29a307e2933cbf67ca9c091941dbdd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210315/_2021031518234140349.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2Fed29a307e2933cbf67ca9c091941dbdd%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210315%2F_2021031518234140349.jpg&h=b23a536f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/none/16b47500c1bf8f81fd9d7217228fa496/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210315/_2021031518414563004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F16b47500c1bf8f81fd9d7217228fa496%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210315%2F_2021031518414563004.jpg&h=85a53c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名內地來港女網民獲派青衣長亨邨單位。小紅書網民圖片<br />\n<br />\n一名內地來港定居的女網民，在網上展示獲分配公屋的信件，稱不用再與家婆同住，引來部分網民爭議，批評政府讓未住滿7年的新移民優先獲派公屋不公平。面對網民攻擊，當事人反駁指，她從2013年已經提交申請，按程序等了超過7年。<br />\n<br />\n內地社交平台「小紅書」上，一名女網民上載一張3月11日房委會通知收件人獲編配青衣長亨邨亨麗樓的信件，並以簡體字寫道「終於派到心儀單位，因為我沒派屋之前也住這裡跟家婆同住！現在居然派給我同邨同樓同層」，形容「感覺自己太好運了」。<br />\n<br />\n結果帖文惹來多個facebook群組的網民攻擊，有人指很多港人輪候公屋十幾年都未上樓，批評納稅人的資源不應先讓新移民優先調遷；也有人指當事人既然本身已經住公屋，沒有優先分配的迫切性，應該先讓其他家庭上樓。<br />\n<br />\n當事人隨後發文反駁，指「我是2013年12月申請的香港公屋！沒有優先調遷。完全是按規定正常排隊」。她說，最初是2人家庭申請，到了2018年連同兩個嬰兒就變4人家庭。她又指，房委會正在分派2013年12月提交的「擴展市區」申請，批評網民「沒核實的就請不要張口就噴，自重點好」。<br />\n<br />\n按房委會的目標，一般公屋申請平均輪候時間為約3年，但截至去年底，一般申請者的平均輪候時間為5.7年，而長者一人申請者的平均輪候時間為3.4年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/none/37b0cfd58c44301fa20df61e3f39a96e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210315/_2021031516370236140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F37b0cfd58c44301fa20df61e3f39a96e%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210315%2F_2021031516370236140.jpg&h=a3bc8695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地來港女網民強調是在2013年已經申請公屋。小紅書網民圖片"},{"pid":"2e53c5960a3e7b414804583450f9fc0ac1f04718","tid":2447739,"uid":55493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"兩個嬰兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6667acbbe0f9c3f0d719cdfebd3b1bec9fddf705","tid":2447739,"uid":23104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:00:17.000Z","msg":"屌 死大陸閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9735a3c66ef1f884e411cb1e2d1ed423e3d1b9c","tid":2447739,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:12:10.000Z","msg":"去邊投訴 咁撚串"},{"pid":"6e48458eb20591b4df36ea1fde6b429d586dda84","tid":2447739,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://666kb.com/i/df6jyhh9sd0s133xm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F666kb.com%2Fi%2Fdf6jyhh9sd0s133xm.jpg&h=2cf1cd01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98aafe5d6832e3e122d7e21f4af6bb496894cca1","tid":2447739,"uid":360241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"腥香港人叫人自重喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e52b954f3ffb7a4daa493fefceb1f01d92f6ba5","tid":2447739,"uid":277254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:45:26.000Z","msg":"公屋又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe316a106df7a58c910f34af49885bc2b2f361af","tid":2447739,